{"tid":284252,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，我好耐之後整左個「泡菜狗部隊鍋」","createTime":"2017-06-14T18:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T10:22:45.000Z","uid":68594,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4620a226aaad3b7d445d950e424715181d3a18","tid":284252,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:22:32.000Z","msg":"話說依排真係冇乜驚為天人嘅作品<br />\n所以唯有整啲狗食既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/021937_1dc3c445ed21578ac364e720b3c9e7bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F021937_1dc3c445ed21578ac364e720b3c9e7bf.jpg&h=bd87694f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n材料（兩-三人份）<br />\n韓式辛辣麵：兩個<br />\n午餐肉：識食一定食一罐<br />\n洋蔥：半隻<br />\n蒜頭：五至六瓣<br />\n椰菜：半隻<br />\n韓式年糕：大約半包<br />\n韓式甜辣醬：二大湯匙<br />\n芝士：兩片<br />\n焗豆：一細罐裝<br />\n雞蛋：一隻<br />\n煙肉：兩片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n製作過程就唔講啦！基本上就係狗屎垃圾都掉撚晒落去就岩架啦！如果有新意啲你可以車件芝士蛋糕落去都可以嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/022104_2d3c82f0ae40db2304e79931dbfb9253.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F022104_2d3c82f0ae40db2304e79931dbfb9253.jpg&h=96cf8141&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實男仔就真係唔難食嘅！公仔麵點會難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過買到二百幾蚊一部就真係癡鳩撚線，今次好正常所以冇乜嘢好講啦！完！"},{"pid":"01aa1dd46a1a92ae5798bea9190d1fc893fcc430","tid":284252,"uid":75694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"無拉絲 無紫薯 唔掂窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c8039b147069fec9c446751a63272efc1a7e32","tid":284252,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無拉絲 無紫薯 唔掂窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有拉絲，沒紫薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依排腦閉塞，其實想整紫薯炒飯，不過我驚自己食唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1ee63416912af5913474aa27b3baea0e802329","tid":284252,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無拉絲 無紫薯 唔掂窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有拉絲，沒紫薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依排腦閉塞，其實想整紫薯炒飯，不過我驚自己食唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你食唔食得曬呢個鍋"},{"pid":"39842e8f97cb82a4a73aa8acca43291dc76ed8eb","tid":284252,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無拉絲 無紫薯 唔掂窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有拉絲，沒紫薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依排腦閉塞，其實想整紫薯炒飯，不過我驚自己食唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你食唔食得曬呢個鍋</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n食得哂啊，4個人既情況下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5d6f6d967057f2de1ee190d01cd2793b2d2ca0","tid":284252,"uid":51484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:43:00.000Z","msg":"其實真係想知點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水要預幾多？<br />\n兩大湯匙隻湯匙有幾大？(試過跟著youtube果個丁丁落2湯匙整辣年糕。好淡同得個辣字。無咩甜或咸味)<br />\n有冇話落邊樣先會好啲？"},{"pid":"50f70157af76c838813565d4f1fc23c8afb90906","tid":284252,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:53:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實真係想知點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水要預幾多？<br />\n兩大湯匙隻湯匙有幾大？(試過跟著youtube果個丁丁落2湯匙整辣年糕。好淡同得個辣字。無咩甜或咸味)<br />\n有冇話落邊樣先會好啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1.通常就煎左啲煙肉先，再落椰菜洋蔥炒到軟身，啲水啱啱好過咗啲椰菜同洋蔥就得架啦，佢哋自己會出水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.起碼呢個大細<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/025210_8cc78d89a961a0fa006fdaa612c311ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F025210_8cc78d89a961a0fa006fdaa612c311ed.jpg&h=a8f7cca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n通常會落買包辛辣麵味粉落去，不過口味就好個人，我會建議煮完唔辛辣啦先再加"},{"pid":"25937460688857afad6be147870c17774c83d7a9","tid":284252,"uid":74883,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實真係想知點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水要預幾多？<br />\n兩大湯匙隻湯匙有幾大？(試過跟著youtube果個丁丁落2湯匙整辣年糕。好淡同得個辣字。無咩甜或咸味)<br />\n有冇話落邊樣先會好啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1.通常就煎左啲煙肉先，再落椰菜洋蔥炒到軟身，啲水啱啱好過咗啲椰菜同洋蔥就得架啦，佢哋自己會出水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.起碼呢個大細<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/025210_8cc78d89a961a0fa006fdaa612c311ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F025210_8cc78d89a961a0fa006fdaa612c311ed.jpg&h=a8f7cca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n通常會落買包辛辣麵味粉落去，不過口味就好個人，我會建議煮完唔辛辣啦先再加</blockquote><br />\n痴線，第一次見人答人大小可以乜比較都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼知你個匙羹幾大"},{"pid":"f7afd03e3d252c8e2c1ece2342b96771ed1dc550","tid":284252,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:18:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實真係想知點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水要預幾多？<br />\n兩大湯匙隻湯匙有幾大？(試過跟著youtube果個丁丁落2湯匙整辣年糕。好淡同得個辣字。無咩甜或咸味)<br />\n有冇話落邊樣先會好啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1.通常就煎左啲煙肉先，再落椰菜洋蔥炒到軟身，啲水啱啱好過咗啲椰菜同洋蔥就得架啦，佢哋自己會出水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.起碼呢個大細<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/025210_8cc78d89a961a0fa006fdaa612c311ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F025210_8cc78d89a961a0fa006fdaa612c311ed.jpg&h=a8f7cca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n通常會落買包辛辣麵味粉落去，不過口味就好個人，我會建議煮完唔辛辣啦先再加</blockquote><br />\n痴線，第一次見人答人大小可以乜比較都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼知你個匙羹幾大</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n你岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唯一搵到可以比較嘅，就係呢支美極，好似係細size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/031841_bee27f33ba399aebe3dffee6cfe338f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F031841_bee27f33ba399aebe3dffee6cfe338f1.jpg&h=26de3f91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9542f47bfabfe569fde99b32e35fcaf4d52a737","tid":284252,"uid":60858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T19:58:45.000Z","msg":"巴打仲有無其他煮過嘅post嚟睇下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e5bd60cdfdcdbfb80db9a39ed544eda94eac64","tid":284252,"uid":15008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T20:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實真係想知點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水要預幾多？<br />\n兩大湯匙隻湯匙有幾大？(試過跟著youtube果個丁丁落2湯匙整